Tiong-iong5 chai-iaN2 chit e5 i3-su3, na7-si7 i tiam7-tiam7 long2 bo5 in3, Lo5 Chip-su7 koh ke3-siok8 kong2,“In ia7 kong2, chhin-chhiuN7 it-poaN e5 po3-choa2, a2-si7 kau3-hoe7 e5 x x po3, chia e5 lan2 e5 hoe7-iu2 long2 u7 lang5 teng7-iat8, chiah ma5-hoan5 li2 khi3 in chhu3 khoaN3; kan-ta Kau3-hoe7 Kong-po3 kap Eng5-kong po3 chiu7 ho2, in-ui7 chit nng7 e5 khan-but8 si7 lan2 TiuN2-lo2 Kau3-hoe7 bo5 boe7 eng7-tit e5; na7 an2-ni, chit8 ni5 oe7 thang seng2 kui2-na7 pah khou, m7-chai li2 e5 i3-kian3 an2-choaN2?” 
